    {
      "name": "Innate Spellcasting (Psionics)",
      "type": "feat",
      "data": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"1598\" > <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Innate Spellcasting (Psionics).</span></span> <p>The thought spy's innate spellcasting ability is Intelligence (spell save DC <span class=\"rd__dc\">13</span>). The thought spy can innately cast the following spells, requiring no components:</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><ul class=\"rd__list rd__list-hang-notitle\"><li class=\"rd__li  rd__li-spell\"><p>At will: @spell[charm person], @spell[disguise self], @spell[encode thoughts|GGR] (see chapter 2)</p></li><li class=\"rd__li  rd__li-spell\"><p>1/day each: @spell[blur], @spell[detect thoughts], @spell[gaseous form]</p></li></ul></div><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>",
